      <title>欧盟财长敦促谨慎报复特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/eu-finance-chiefs-urge-caution-in-retaliation-over-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟财长警告称，在唐纳德·特朗普返回白宫后，欧盟不要采取过激行动来应对特朗普对欧盟产品征收关税的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/eu-finance-chiefs-urge-caution-in-retaliation-over-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 16:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉马杜罗向边境派遣军队 数千人逃离哥伦比亚 恐怖主义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/maduro-sends-troops-to-border-as-thousands-flee-colombia-terror</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于哥伦比亚主要可卡因产区之一的战斗造成了一场人道主义灾难，委内瑞拉将加强边境安全部队的存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/maduro-sends-troops-to-border-as-thousands-flee-colombia-terror</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 16:11:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多诺霍称欧洲需要就德拉吉报告采取更紧急的行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/europe-needs-to-act-more-urgently-on-draghi-report-donohoe-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区高级官员表示，欧盟需要加快努力提高竞争力，并实施欧洲央行行长马里奥·德拉吉提出的一些建议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/europe-needs-to-act-more-urgently-on-draghi-report-donohoe-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 15:21:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京称俄罗斯愿意与特朗普就乌克兰问题进行对话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/putin-says-russia-is-open-to-dialogue-on-ukraine-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京表示，俄罗斯已准备好与美国就乌克兰战争进行谈判，并祝贺新任总统唐纳德·特朗普的就职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/putin-says-russia-is-open-to-dialogue-on-ukraine-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 14:28:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普暂缓对华征收关税，呼吁进行研究</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/trump-seen-sparing-china-targeted-tariffs-on-day-one-of-new-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普不会在上任第一天公布针对中国的关税，因为新一届政府将首先与北京进行潜在接触，而不是展开另一场贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/trump-seen-sparing-china-targeted-tariffs-on-day-one-of-new-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 14:21:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划在美国边境宣布国家紧急状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/trump-plans-sweeping-executive-action-designed-to-close-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普计划采取全面的新行政措施，旨在打击非法越境行为并针对已经在美国境内的无证移民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/trump-plans-sweeping-executive-action-designed-to-close-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 14:21:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国拒绝北爱尔兰统一主义者要求绕过部分欧盟规则的呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/uk-rejects-ni-unionists-call-to-pull-eu-deal-s-stormont-brake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府拒绝了北爱尔兰统一党派提出的豁免北爱尔兰部分欧盟规则的请求，此举有可能激怒那些主张与英国其他地区加强联系的团体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/uk-rejects-ni-unionists-call-to-pull-eu-deal-s-stormont-brake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 13:51:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登赦免米利、福奇、切尼和其他特朗普目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/biden-pardons-trump-targets-milley-fauci-and-cheney</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁要惩罚的政府高级官员予以先发制人的赦免，以防止其继任者对他所称的政治敌人进行的潜在报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/biden-pardons-trump-targets-milley-fauci-and-cheney</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 12:19:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将宣布国家能源紧急状态，释放新权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/trump-to-declare-national-energy-emergency-unlocking-new-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普准备启动紧急权力，下令采取一系列措施，以释放国内能源生产潜力，并取消拜登时代应对气候变化的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/trump-to-declare-national-energy-emergency-unlocking-new-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 03:35:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥如何应对特朗普大规模驱逐的承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/how-mexico-is-preparing-for-trump-s-promises-of-mass-deportations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆正在全力支持居住在美国的大约 500 万非法墨西哥人。她的政府为被拘留者推出了一款紧急应用程序，安排了 2,600 多名律师和近 2,200 名领事馆工作人员，她的外交部长会见了每个边境州的官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/how-mexico-is-preparing-for-trump-s-promises-of-mass-deportations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
